Not Riding Your Bike to Austin??  Participate Anyway!!!
Support TEAM ENRON and Jeff Skilling by participating in the MS150 from
Houston to Austin on April 21st and April 22nd.  All-purpose volunteers are
needed to handle such various and sundry logistical duties as serving meals
to the Team, playing music as a DJ, directing riders to the Enron Tent,
setting-up and tearing-down, making massage appointments... to name just a
